Materials</p><div class="sppb-addon-content"></div></div></div></div><div id="sppb-addon-wrapper-1669535190236" class="sppb-addon-wrapper"><div id="sppb-addon-1669535190236" class="clearfix "     ><div class="sppb-icon  sppb-text-center sppb-icon-hover-effect-zoom-in"><span class="sppb-icon-inner"><i class="fas fa-dollar-sign" aria-hidden="true"></i></span></div></div></div><div id="sppb-addon-wrapper-1669535190237" class="sppb-addon-wrapper"><div id="sppb-addon-1669535190237" class="clearfix "     ><div class="sppb-addon sppb-addon-text-block sppb-text-center "><p class="sppb-addon-title">100% Money-Back <br>Guarantee</p><div class="sppb-addon-content"></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div id="section-id-1669708493574" class="sppb-section" ><div class="sppb-container-inner"><div class="sppb-row"><div class="sppb-col-md-12" id="column-wrap-id-1669708493575"><div id="column-id-1669708493575" class="sppb-column" ><div class="sppb-column-addons"><div id="sppb-addon-wrapper-1669535190232" class="sppb-addon-wrapper"><div id="sppb-addon-1669535190232" class="clearfix "     ><div class="sppb-text-center"><a href="/contact" id="btn-1669535190232" class="sppb-btn  sppb-btn-default sppb-btn-lg sppb-btn-rounded">FREE INSPECTION NOW</a></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></section><section id="section-id-1669364928547" class="sppb-section" ><div class="sppb-row-container"><div class="sppb-row"><div class="sppb-col-md-6" id="column-wrap-id-1669364928544"><div id="column-id-1669364928544" class="sppb-column" ><div class="sppb-column-addons"><div id="sppb-addon-wrapper-1669364928652" class="sppb-addon-wrapper"><div id="sppb-addon-1669364928652" class="clearfix "     ><div class="sppb-addon sppb-addon-single-image sppb-text-center "><div class="sppb-addon-content"><div class="sppb-addon-single-image-container"><img class="sppb-img-responsive" src="/images/00-pesco/home/pesco-employees-good-at-eliminate-pest-problem-that-spread-diseases.jpeg"  alt="pesco employees good at eliminate pest problem that spread diseases" title=""   loading="lazy"></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="sppb-col-md-6" id="column-wrap-id-1669364928545"><div id="column-id-1669364928545" class="sppb-column" ><div class="sppb-column-addons"><div id="sppb-addon-wrapper-1669711160006" class="sppb-addon-wrapper"><div id="sppb-addon-1669711160006" class=" sppb-wow fadeIn clearfix "  data-sppb-wow-duration="1800ms" data-sppb-wow-delay="300ms"     ><div class="sppb-addon sppb-addon-header text-style-004  sppb-text-left"><h3 class="sppb-addon-title">Pesco's Expert</h3></div></div></div><div id="sppb-addon-wrapper-1669364928655" class="sppb-addon-wrapper"><div id="sppb-addon-1669364928655" class=" sppb-wow fadeIn clearfix "  data-sppb-wow-duration="1800ms" data-sppb-wow-delay="550ms"     ><div class="sppb-addon sppb-addon-text-block  header-style-002"><h2 class="sppb-addon-title"><strong>Pest Control</strong> Services</h2><div class="sppb-addon-content"><div style="text-align: justify;">
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">A pest is defined as any organism which is detrimental to a human or his activities in some way. Most insects or animals are considered pests because they are disease carriers and cause a certain degree of disruption to our daily activities. Nevertheless, some insects or animals are recognized as pests just because they create fear towards humans, e.g. rats.</span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Pesco specialist will access the pest infestation level of your properties and advice you on the control measurements. We ensure the customized program is based on your need and implemented in the most effective way.</span></p>
</div></div></div></div></div><div id="section-id-1670574816790" class="sppb-section" ><div class="sppb-container-inner"><div class="sppb-row"><div class="sppb-col-md-4" id="column-wrap-id-1670574816791"><div id="column-id-1670574816791" class="sppb-column" ><div class="sppb-column-addons"><div id="sppb-addon-wrapper-1669364928489" class="sppb-addon-wrapper"><div id="sppb-addon-1669364928489" class="clearfix "     ><div class="sppb-addon sppb-addon-single-image sppb-text-center "><div class="sppb-addon-content"><div class="sppb-addon-single-image-container"><img class="sppb-img-responsive" src="/images/00-pesco/articles/cockroaches.jpg"  alt="cockroach control" title=""   loading="lazy"></div></div></div></div></div><div id="sppb-addon-wrapper-1669364928700" class="sppb-addon-wrapper"><div id="sppb-addon-1669364928700" class=" sppb-wow fadeIn clearfix "  data-sppb-wow-duration="1800ms" data-sppb-wow-delay="100ms"     ><div class="sppb-addon sppb-addon-text-block sppb-text-center "><h3 class="sppb-addon-title">Cockroach Control</h3><div class="sppb-addon-content"></div></div></div></div><div id="sppb-addon-wrapper-1669364928494" class="sppb-addon-wrapper"><div id="sppb-addon-1669364928494" class="clearfix "     ><div class="sppb-addon sppb-addon-single-image sppb-text-center "><div class="sppb-addon-content"><div class="sppb-addon-single-image-container"><img class="sppb-img-responsive" src="/images/00-pesco/articles/flies.jpg"  alt="flies control" title=""   loading="lazy"></div></div></div></div></div><div id="sppb-addon-wrapper-1669364928495" class="sppb-addon-wrapper"><div id="sppb-addon-1669364928495" class=" sppb-wow fadeIn clearfix "  data-sppb-wow-duration="1800ms" data-sppb-wow-delay="100ms"     ><div class="sppb-addon sppb-addon-text-block sppb-text-center "><h3 class="sppb-addon-title">Flies<br>Control</h3><div class="sppb-addon-content"></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="sppb-col-md-4" id="column-wrap-id-1670574816794"><div id="column-i