iv id="column-id-1670479893043" class="sppb-column" ><div class="sppb-column-addons"><div id="sppb-addon-wrapper-1670479892808" class="sppb-addon-wrapper"><div id="sppb-addon-1670479892808" class="clearfix "     ><div class="sppb-addon sppb-addon-single-image sppb-text-center "><div class="sppb-addon-content"><div class="sppb-addon-single-image-container"><img class="sppb-img-responsive" src="/images/00-pesco/home/logo/haccp-logo.webp"  alt="haccp logo" title="" width="115" height="115" loading="lazy"></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="sppb-col-md-3" id="column-wrap-id-1670479893044"><div id="column-id-1670479893044" class="sppb-column" ><div class="sppb-column-addons"><div id="sppb-addon-wrapper-1670479892810" class="sppb-addon-wrapper"><div id="sppb-addon-1670479892810" class="clearfix "     ><div class="sppb-addon sppb-addon-single-image sppb-text-center "><div class="sppb-addon-content"><div class="sppb-addon-single-image-container"><img class="sppb-img-responsive" src="/images/00-pesco/home/logo/halal-malaysia-logo.webp"  alt="halal malaysia logo" title="" width="120" height="120" loading="lazy"></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="sppb-col-md-3" id="column-wrap-id-1670479893045"><div id="column-id-1670479893045" class="sppb-column" ><div class="sppb-column-addons"><div id="sppb-addon-wrapper-1670479892812" class="sppb-addon-wrapper"><div id="sppb-addon-1670479892812" class="clearfix "     ><div class="sppb-addon sppb-addon-single-image sppb-text-center "><div class="sppb-addon-content"><div class="sppb-addon-single-image-container"><img class="sppb-img-responsive" src="/images/00-pesco/home/logo/iso-banner.webp"  alt="iso banner" title="" width="114" height="41" loading="lazy"></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="sppb-col-md-3" id="column-wrap-id-1670479893046"><div id="column-id-1670479893046" class="sppb-column" ><div class="sppb-column-addons"><div id="sppb-addon-wrapper-1670479892814" class="sppb-addon-wrapper"><div id="sppb-addon-1670479892814" class="clearfix "     ><div class="sppb-addon sppb-addon-single-image sppb-text-center "><div class="sppb-addon-content"><div class="sppb-addon-single-image-container"><img class="sppb-img-responsive" src="/images/00-pesco/home/logo/mesti-logo.webp"  alt="mesti logo" title="" width="114" height="53" loading="lazy"></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></section><section id="section-id-1669446788454" class="sppb-section" ><div class="sppb-row-container"><div class="sppb-row"><div class="sppb-col-md-12" id="column-wrap-id-1669446788453"><div id="column-id-1669446788453" class="sppb-column" ><div class="sppb-column-addons"><div id="sppb-addon-wrapper-1669705675595" class="sppb-addon-wrapper"><div id="sppb-addon-1669705675595" class="clearfix "     ><div class="sppb-addon sppb-addon-header text-style-003 header-style-003 sppb-text-center"><h3 class="sppb-addon-title"><span><strong>Certification </strong>& Membership</span></h3></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="sppb-col-md-4" id="column-wrap-id-1669446788457"><div id="column-id-1669446788457" class="sppb-column" ><div class="sppb-column-addons"></div></div></div><div class="sppb-col-md-4" id="column-wrap-id-1669446788458"><div id="column-id-1669446788458" class="sppb-column" ><div class="sppb-column-addons"><div id="sppb-addon-wrapper-1669446788462" class="sppb-addon-wrapper"><div id="sppb-addon-1669446788462" class="clearfix "     ><div id="sppb-modal-1669446788462" class="mfp-hide white-popup-block"><div class="modal-inner-block"><div style="text-align: justify;">
<div class="sG">
<div class="EH zB vF">
<div class="tatsu-module tatsu-HF-zFxvYW h5 UI VI FB">
<div class="sG">
<div class="EH zB vF">
<div class="tatsu-module tatsu-HF-zFxvYW h5 UI VI FB">
<div class="tatsu-module tatsu-hw-Vgq0j0 tatsu-module SH sB">
<h3><span style="font-weight: 400;">ISO 9001</span></h3>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">ISO stand for International Organization for Standardization. It is the world’s largest developer and publisher of international standards. It contributes to making the development, manufacturing and supply of products and services more efficient, safer and cleaner. It also serves to safeguard consumers and users of products and services.</span></p>
<h3><span style="font-weight: 400;">The United Kingdom Accreditation Service (UKAS)</span></h3>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">The United Kingdom Accreditation Service (UKAS) is the national accreditation body from the United Kingdom, appointed by governments to assess organisations that provide certification, testing, inspection and calibration services.</span></p>
<h3><span style="font-weight: 400;">The International Accreditation Forum (IAF)</span></h3>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">The International Accreditation Forum (IAF) is a worldwide association of accreditation bodies and other bodies interested in conformity assessment in the fields of management systems, products, processes, services, personnel, validation and verification and other similar programmes of conformity assessment.</span></p>
<h3><span style="font-weight: 400;">NPMA Membership</span></h3>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Pesco Pest Control is a member of the National Pest Control Association (NPMA), ensuring that we are up to speed on the newest pest management innovations. The expertise gained via the NPMA's numerous programmes will help us provide better and higher-quality services to our consumers.</span></p>
<h3 class="GH tatsu-align-left bG GB TB"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Government Licensing</span></h3>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Our qualified technicians are licenced under the Ministry of Agriculture and Pesticides Act 1974 for our clients' peace of mind. The Ministry of Agriculture has registered and authorized the products we utilize. They're effective, safe, and ecologically friendly.</span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Pest control is our first focus, so you don't have to be concerned. We work hard to be on the leading edge of the industry to provide you with the most effective and cost-efficient solutions possible. To provide top-notch service, our employees get frequent training and follow-up education. You should, in theory, never have to worry about pests or the damage they bring to your home after you hire our crew.</span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Unlike other firms who make grand promises to their clients but fail to deliver, Pesco does. From top management to on-site personnel, every member of our team reads our commitment and commits to maintaining every aspect of it every day they come to work.</span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Our company recognizes that your house and business are the most important things to you. When bugs infiltrate your home, it may make your family and customers feel unpleasant. It might also result in costly damage that you aren't prepared to cope with. As a result, Pesco promises to work as hard as possible to return your property to the state you want. This involves paying close attention to the smallest details when developing a pest control solution that works for you. Pesco is recognized for using the industry-leading Integrated Pest Management approach, which reduces material use while maximizing outcomes. Call Pesco now at 012-800 7008 or 07-562 0256 for a FREE, NO-OBLIGATION estimate or schedule online to discover more about what we can do for you!</span></p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div></div></div><div class=" sppb-text-center"><a class="sppb-btn  sppb-btn-default sppb-btn-xlg sppb-btn-rounded sppb-btn-flat sppb-magnific-popup sppb-modal-selector" data-popup_type="inline" data-mainclass="mfp-no-margins mfp-with-zoom" href="#sppb-modal-1669446788462" id="sppb-modal-1669446788462-selector">VIEW CERTS</a></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="sppb-col-md-4" id="column-wrap-id-1669446788459"><div id="column-id-1669446788459" class="sppb-column" ><div class="sppb-column-addons"></div></div></div></div></div></section><section id="section-id-1669446788473" class="sppb-section" ><div class="sppb-row-container"><div class="sppb-row"><div class="sppb-col-md-6" id="column-wrap-id-1669446788471"><div id="column-id-1669446788471" class="sppb-column" ><div class="sppb-column-addons"><div id="sppb-addon-wrapper-1669708493692" class="sppb-addon-wrapper"><div id="sppb-addon-1669708493692" class=" sppb-wow fadeIn clearfix "  data-sppb-wow-duration="1800ms" data-sppb-wow-delay="300ms"     ><div class="sppb-addon sppb-addon-header heading-pattern-002 sppb-text-left"><h3 class="sppb-addon-title">What We Do</h3></div></div></div><div id="sppb-addon-wrapper-1669705675550" class="sppb-addon-wrapper"><div id="sppb-addon-1669705675550" class=" sppb-wow fadeIn clearfix "  data-sppb-wow-duration="1800ms" data-sppb-wow-delay="550ms"     ><div class="sppb-addon sppb-addon-text-block sppb-text-left header-style-002"><h2 class="sppb-addon-title"><strong>We Deliver</strong> the Best<br> <strong>Pest Control Services</strong> in Malaysia and Singapore</h2><div class="sppb-addon-content"><div style="text-align: justify;">
<p>Pesco is an expert in pest control which focus on providing 3E pest management solutions to home and businesses at affordable prices. We build healthy surroundings and provide peace of mind for both people and company owners via preventive, innovative technology, and long-term solutions.</p>
<p>With over 20 years of cumulative pest-control knowledge, our experienced staffs confidently offer custom-tailored solutions surpassing industry standards. We proudly put our name behind every project we perform, regardless of the size or whether you're seeking residential or commercial support.</p>
</div></div></div></div></div><div id="sppb-addon-wrapper-1669705675551" class="sppb-addon-wrapper"><div id="sppb-addon-1669705675551" class=" sppb-wow fadeIn clearfix "  data-sppb-wow-duration="1900ms" data-sppb-wow-delay="700ms"     ><div class="sppb-text-center"><a href="/pest-control" id="btn-1669705675551" class="sppb-btn  sppb-btn-default sppb-btn-rounded">Read More</a></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="sppb-col-md-6" id="column-wrap-id-1669446788472"><div id="column-id-1669446788472" class="sppb-column" ><div class="sppb-column-addons"><div id="sppb-addon-wrapper-1669446788476" class="sppb-addon-wrapper"><div id="sppb-addon-1669446788476" class="clearfix "     ><div class="sppb-addon sppb-addon-single-image sppb-text-center "><div class="sppb-addon-content"><div class="sppb-addon-single-image-container"><img class="sppb-img-responsive" src="/images/00-pesco/home/pesco-employee-good-at-cutting-edge-technology.jpeg"  alt="pesco employee good at using cutting edge technology" title=""   loading="lazy"></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></section><section id="section-id-1670483056400" class="sppb-section" ><div class="sppb-row-container"><div class="sppb-row"><div class="sppb-col-md-12" id="column-wrap-id-1670483056464"><div id="column-id-1670483056464" class="sppb-column" ><div class="sppb-column-addons"><div id="sppb-addon-wrapper-1670483056465" class="sppb-addon-wrapper"><div id="sppb-addon-1670483056465" class="clearfix "     ><div class="sppb-addon sppb-addon-header header-style-002 sppb-text-center"><h2 class="sppb-addon-title"><strong>Authorized Applicator </strong>& Technological Collaboration</h2></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="sppb-col-md-6" id="column-wrap-id-1670487411493"><div id="column-id-1670487411493" class="sppb-column" ><div class="sppb-column-addons"><div id="section-id-1670483056466" class="sppb-section" ><div class="sppb-container-inner"><div class="sppb-row"><div class="sppb-col-md-3" id